#

Orange Almond Cake

$15
320 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

NutsEggs

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeVegetarian

Tags:

DessertCakesBaking

Description

A moist and fragrant cake made with fresh oranges and almond flour, perfect for a delightful dessert or afternoon treat.

Ingredients

  • Almond flour: 2 cups
  • Granulated sugar: 1 cup
  • Fresh oranges (zest and juice): 2
  • Eggs: 4
  • Baking powder: 1 tsp
  • Salt: 1/2 tsp
  • Butter (melted): 1/2 cup
  • Powdered sugar (for dusting): to taste
